            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EHabakkuk%201%3A1-3%3A19%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22haba_1_1%22%20bk%3D%22haba%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EHabakkuk%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20message%20that%20the%20prophet%20Habakkuk%20received%20in%20a%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22haba_1_2%22%20bk%3D%22haba%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EHabakkuk%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Complaint%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EHow%20long%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20must%20I%20call%20for%20help%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EBut%20you%20do%20not%20listen!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BViolence%20is%20everywhere!%26%23x201D%3B%20I%20cry%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20you%20do%20not%20come%20to%20save.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22haba_1_3%22%20bk%3D%22haba%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EMust%20I%20forever%20see%20these%20evil%20deeds%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWhy%20must%20I%20watch%20all%20this%20misery%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EWherever%20I%20look%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%20see%20destruction%20and%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EI%20am%20surrounded%20by%20people%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewho%20love%20to%20argue%20and%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22haba_1_4%22%20bk%3D%22haba%22%20ch%3D%221%22