nd%20violent%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20will%20march%20across%20the%20world%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20conquer%20other%20lands.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22haba_1_7%22%20bk%3D%22haba%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20are%20notorious%20for%20their%20cruelty%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20do%20whatever%20they%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22haba_1_8%22%20bk%3D%22haba%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3ETheir%20horses%20are%20swifter%20than%20cheetahs%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A8%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Eleopards.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20fiercer%20than%20wolves%20at%20dusk.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ETheir%20charioteers%20charge%20from%20far%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ELike%20eagles%2C%20they%20swoop%20down%20to%20devour%20their%20prey.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22haba_1_9%22%20bk%3D%22haba%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BOn%20they%20come%2C%20all%20bent%20on%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ETheir%20hordes%20advance%20like%20a%20desert%20wind%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Esweeping%20captives%20ahead%20of%20them%20like%20sand.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22haba_1_10%22%20bk%3D%22haba%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20scoff%20at%20kings%20and%20princes%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20scorn%20all%20their%20fortresses.%3C%2Fp%